arded as an (almost) [&hellip;]</p>\n","author":{"name":"Louise Wood","slug":"louise-wood","avatar":{"url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08b72de95886dc800efe0347f324f87a?s=100&d=mm&r=g"}},"tags":{"nodes":[{"name":"#XtheHaze","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/xthehaze/","slug":"xthehaze"},{"name":"Climate Change","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/climate-change/","slug":"climate-change"},{"name":"Forest","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/forest/","slug":"forest"},{"name":"Haze","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/haze/","slug":"haze"},{"name":"Palm Oil","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/palm-oil/","slug":"palm-oil"}]},"categories":{"nodes":[{"name":"Climate Change","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/category/climate-change/","slug":"climate-change"},{"name":"Haze","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/category/haze/","slug":"haze"}]},"campaigns":{"nodes":[]},"featuredImage":{"sourceUrl":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/RiauProject.png","altText":"","srcSet":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/RiauProject-300x117.png 300w, https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/RiauProject-768x298.png 768w, https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/RiauProject-1024x398.png 1024w, https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/RiauProject.png 1591w"}},{"id":"cG9zdDoxODk=","title":"NEA triggers the Transboundary Haze Pollution Act","uri":"nea-triggers-the-transboundary-haze-pollution-act/","slug":"nea-triggers-the-transboundary-haze-pollution-act","date":"2015-09-28T07:30:13","content":"<p>Minister for the Environment Mr Vivian Balakrishnan has announced details on his Facebook account of the first companies to be served notice under the Transboundary Haze Pollution Act. The Minister also announced the government&#8217;s intentions to review its procurement procedure saying they would be taking measures to ensure where possible their suppliers followed internationally recognised [&hellip;]</p>\n","author":{"name":"Louise Wood","slug":"louise-wood","avatar":{"url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08b72de95886dc800efe0347f324f87a?s=100&d=mm&r=g"}},"tags":{"nodes":[{"name":"#XtheHaze","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/xthehaze/","slug":"xthehaze"},{"name":"Haze","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/haze/","slug":"haze"},{"name":"Transboundary Haze Pollution Act","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/transboundary-haze-pollution-act/","slug":"transboundary-haze-pollution-act"}]},"categories":{"nodes":[{"name":"Forest","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/category/forest/","slug":"forest"},{"name":"Haze","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/category/haze/","slug":"haze"}]},"campaigns":{"nodes":[]},"featuredImage":{"sourceUrl":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/hazy.jpg","altText":"","srcSet":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/hazy-300x97.jpg 300w, https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/hazy-768x248.jpg 768w, https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/hazy-1024x331.jpg 1024w, https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/hazy.jpg 1548w"}},{"id":"cG9zdDoxNTY=","title":"Should Your Child Wear a Haze Mask?","uri":"child-haze-mask/","slug":"child-haze-mask","date":"2015-09-15T00:59:37","content":"<p>You might have seen us recently giving out N95 masks in the streets with the help of our campaign partners. Giving out the masks is an opportunity to meet and listen to Singaporeans and visitors to our country. One tourist told us he would not come back to Singapore again during the haze season. But [&hellip;]</p>\n","author":{"name":"Louise Wood","slug":"louise-wood","avatar":{"url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08b72de95886dc800efe0347f324f87a?s=100&d=mm&r=g"}},"tags":{"nodes":[{"name":"#XtheHaze","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.p